## 6) Quick Validations

### Python compile check
```powershell
python -m py_compile pinescript-agents/tools/gexbot_pull_historical.py pinescript-agents/tools/gexbot_nq_to_pine_block.py pinescript-agents/tools/gexbot_refresh_multi_asset_strategy.py
```

### Pipeline script parse check
```powershell
$null = [System.Management.Automation.Language.Parser]::ParseFile('pinescript-agents/tools/run_gex_pipeline.ps1',[ref]$null,[ref]$null); if ($?) { 'OK' }
```

